item.title: Rishi Sunak Becomes UK Prime Minister — He Wants to Make Britain a Global Crypto Investment Hub
item.description: Rishi Sunak Becomes UK Prime Minister — He Wants to Make Britain a Global Crypto Investment Hub Britain’s former Chancellor of the Exchequer Rishi Sunak has become the country’s new prime minister, succeeding Liz Truss who resigned after 44 days in office.
